videos.description: Hofstra's Eli Pemberton cannot handle Villanova's Mikal Bridge who speeds past him to bank an easy layup.
videos.headline: Bridges blows past defender for layup

videos.description: Hofstra's Kenny Wormley takes the jumper with ease as he fakes out Villanova's Mikal Bridges.
videos.headline: Wormley fakes out defender for swish

videos.description: Villanova's Malik Bridges blocks Hofstra's Eli Pemberton at the rim then Jalen Brunson takes it all the way back for the basket and a foul.
videos.headline: Villanova block leads to and-1

videos.description: Omari Spellman takes Jalen Brunson's pass and drains an open jumper in the paint.
videos.headline: Spellman knocks it down with confidence

videos.description: Hoftra's Joel Angus III drives to the basket but is met at the rim by Villnova's Malik Bridges who swats his shot out of bounds.
videos.headline: Bridges gets second block of half

videos.description: Hunter Sabety left all alone under the rim and converts Desure Buie's pass from a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Sabety wide open for dunk

videos.description: Phil Booth sends Villanova to halftime with momentum after drilling a 3-pointer right before the buzzer to end the first half.
videos.headline: Booth beats the buzzer with 3-pointer

videos.description: Hofstra's Rokas Gustys does not let Jalen Brunson stop him and easily lays it in for 2 points.
videos.headline: Gustys makes layup over Brunson

videos.description: Hofstra's Justin Wright-Foreman gets an improbable layup to fall as he was double teamed in mid-air.
videos.headline: Wright-Foreman makes acrobatic layup

videos.description: Hofstra's Eli Pemberton cleans off his teammates miss with a clean putback dunk.
videos.headline: Pemberton  jumps for putback dunk
